ongoing
■ adjective continuing; still in progress.
Derivatives
ongoingnessnoun

Từ điển Đồng nghĩa
ongoing
▸ adjective
1negotiations are ongoing: IN PROGRESS, under way, going on, continuing, taking place, proceeding, progressing, advancing; unfinished.
2an ongoing struggle: CONTINUOUS, continuing, uninterrupted, unbroken, non-stop, constant, ceaseless, unceasing, unending, endless, never-ending, unremitting, relentless, unfaltering.
